esh]]<ref name="Trib 20080803">{{cite web|author1=Megha Mann|author2=Jai Kumar|title=146 die in Naina Devi stampede|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2008/20080804/main1.htm|publisher=[[The Tribune (Chandigarh)]]|accessdate=6 July 2014|location=Anandpur Sahib / Bilaspur|date=3 August 2008}}</ref><ref name="DNA 20131015"/> || {{Dts|format=dmy|2008|08|03}} || 146 || 150 |- | [[2008 Naina Devi temple stampede#Reaction|Naina Devi temple, Himachal Pradesh]]<ref name="ToI Bodh">{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-08-04/india/27899904_1_naina-devi-temple-stampede-tragedy|title=30 years ago, similar tragedy at shrine had claimed 65 lives|last=Bodh|first= Anand|publisher=[[The Times of India]]|accessdate=4 August 2008 |date=4 August 2008}}</ref> || {{Dts|format=dmy|1978|08|03}} || 65 || {{Citation needed|date=July 2014|reason=Cite needed for injured count only (others data from cites at left)}} |- | [[2008 Jodhpur stampede|Chamunda Devi temple, Jodhpur, Rajasthan]]<ref name="BBC 20081002">{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/7648104.stm |title=India stampede death toll rises |publisher=[[BBC News]] |location=Jodhpur, India |agency=[[Indo-Asian News Service|IANS]] |date=2 October 2008 |accessdate=6 July 2014}}</ref><ref name="HT 20081003">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?sectionName=HomePage&id=117d1d90-c1bd-4e46-9444-44eb21caca68&&Headline=Temple+stampede+toll+rises+to+224 |title=Death toll in Jodhpur temple stampede rises to 224 |publisher=[[Hindustan Times]] |date=3 October 2008 |accessdate=6 July 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012130713/http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?sectionName=HomePage&id=117d1d90-c1bd-4e46-9444-44eb21caca68&&Headline=Temple+stampede+toll+rises+to+224 |archivedate=12 October 2008 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref name="BG Wax">{{cite web|author1=Emily Wax ([[The Washington Post]])|title=Death toll rises to 168 in Indian stampe